Published: 04 September 2025

Vast and hidden urban methane emissions from the Russia–Ukraine war
                    Zeyu Feng1, Rong Hu1, Yuqing Pan1, Qianjian Xv1, Jing Zhang1, Qingyong Wang1, Kaiqin Cao1, Shufeng Liu1, Alexander Baklanov2, Jens Hesselbjerg Christen 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-9908-82032, Daniel Rosenfeld3, John H. Seinfeld4, Shaocai Yu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-9718-82465,6,7 & …Pengfei Li 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-1542-76591 Show authors

Nature Cities

(2025)Cite this article







